#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/adopt_sentences.ctp#L44
msgid "About adoption"
msgstr "接管說明"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/adopt_sentences.ctp#L48
msgid ""
"Adopting is a way to vote \"this sentence is correct\". It is also an "
"occasion to check the sentence and correct it if there is a mistake."
msgstr "接管可以表示您認為「這個例句正確無誤」，也可以讓您檢查例句，並修正錯誤。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/adopt_sentences.ctp#L58
msgid ""
"So if you want to help us check and correct sentences, then adopt "
"({adoptButton}) any \"orphan\" sentence you see in your <strong>native "
"language</strong>, and correct it if necessary. Read <a "
"href=\"{url}\">this</a> for further explanation."
msgstr "若想協助我們檢查並改正例句，歡迎隨時接管 ({adoptButton}) 屬於您<strong>母語</strong>的例句，必要時進行改正。請參閱<a href=\"{url}\">這篇文章</a>，獲取近一步的說明。"

#. title of the help text on the Adopt sentence page
#. / title of the help text on the Add vocabulary page
#. / title of the sidebar text on the Wall page
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/adopt_sentences.ctp#L74
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Vocabulary/add.ctp#L41
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Wall/index.ctp#L56
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "提示"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/adopt_sentences.ctp#L78
msgid ""
"If you see another username appear after adopting a sentence, it means that "
"someone else adopted the sentence very shortly before you did. In such "
"cases, you can try adopting sentences that are several pages away from your "
"current page to reduce the chances of that happening again."
msgstr "若在接管例句後出現其他使用者的名稱，這表示其他人在不久之前先您一步接管例句。在這種情況下，您可以嘗試從後面幾頁開始接管例句，以避免這種情況的發生。"

#. menu item on the top (verb)
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L28
#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Element/top_menu.ctp#L101
msgid "Improve sentences"
msgstr "改進例句"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L61
msgid "Related links"
msgstr "相關連結"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L63
msgid "Tag guidelines"
msgstr "標籤方針"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L70
msgid "Tags you should know about"
msgstr "您應該了解的標籤"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L72
msgid ""
"The community has come up with several \"utility tags\" to improve the "
"quality and reliability of sentences."
msgstr "我們的社群建立了數種「公用標籤」，來改善例句品質與可靠程度。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L81
msgid "{tagChange}: the sentence needs to be changed."
msgstr "{tagChange}：例句需要修改。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L85
msgid "{tagCheck}: the sentence needs to be checked."
msgstr "{tagCheck}：例句需要核查。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L89
msgid "{tagNNC}: the sentence needs to be checked by a native speaker."
msgstr "{tagNNC}：例句需要母語人士核查。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L93
msgid "{tagOK}: the sentence is considered correct by at least one person."
msgstr "{tagOK}：至少一人認為例句正確無誤。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L102
msgid "How to help"
msgstr "如何協助"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L104
msgid ""
"You need to be an <a href=\"{}\">advanced contributor</a>; otherwise you "
"will not be able to tag sentences."
msgstr "您必須成為<a href=\"{}\">進階參與者</a>，才能為例句新增標籤。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L109
msgid ""
"Whenever you notice a sentence that is wrong or sounds strange, add the tag "
"{tagChange} and post a comment to suggest a correction or better phrasing."
msgstr "只要您發現某個例句不正確或聽起來不自然，就可以新增 {tagChange} 標籤，並留下一則留言，建議修改方式或更好的用詞遣句。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L115
msgid ""
"Whenever you notice a possible mistake, add the tag {tagCheck} and post a "
"comment explaining what you think the mistake may be."
msgstr "只要您發現例句可能有誤，就可以新增 {tagCheck} 標籤，並留下一則留言，說明您認為錯誤出在哪裡。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L121
msgid ""
"Whenever you add a sentence in a foreign language and are not completely "
"sure that it is correct, add the tag {tagNNC}."
msgstr "只要您在新增外語例句時不確定是否正確，就可以新增 {tagNNC} 標籤。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L126
msgid ""
"Whenever you can, browse through sentences that are tagged {tagChange}, "
"{tagCheck}, and {tagNNC} to discuss the sentences with other members and "
"help decide what to do with these sentences."
msgstr "您可以隨時瀏覽擁有 {tagChange}、{tagCheck} 和 {tagNNC} 標籤的例句，與其他成員討論例句，共同決定如何處理這些例句。"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Activities/improve_sentences.ctp#L135
msgid ""
"Once a problematic sentence has been addressed, tag it {tagOK}. More "
"generally, you can browse and check others' sentences and tag them with "
"{tagOK}. But do this only when you are completely sure that they are "
"correct, and do not use the tag on your own sentences."
msgstr "解決完有問題的例句後，請新增 {tagOK} 標籤。一般而言，您可以隨時瀏覽並檢查其他例句，並為其新增 {tagOK} 標籤。但只有在您完全確定例句正確時才可以新增標籤，而且不要在自己的例句上新增此標籤。"

