#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/index.ctp#L93
msgid ""
"The new sentence design will soon completely replace the old one. Please try"
" it out and let us know if you experience any issue. You can enable it with "
"the option \"Display sentences with the new design\" in your Settings."
msgstr "新的例句設計即將完全取代舊設計。請試一試新的設計，並向我們回報您遇到的任何問題。您可以在設定中選擇 [以新設計顯示例句]，來啟用新設計。"

